## Project Structure

```
lib/{{gemName}}/
  client.rb          # Main client class
  http_client.rb     # HTTP layer with retry logic (Faraday)
  auth.rb            # OAuth 2.0 implementation
  pagination.rb      # Pagination enumerator
  errors.rb          # Error class hierarchy
  resources/         # One file per API resource
  types/             # Data model classes
spec/                # Unit tests (RSpec)
  integration/       # Integration tests
docs/                # API documentation per resource
```

## Key Patterns

- Uses Faraday for HTTP requests
- snake_case naming convention
- Keyword arguments for parameters
- Error hierarchy with rescue
- Lazy enumerators for pagination
- Data classes for models

